text:
Jjangmeon taste - good; noodle  cooked a bit too long.
Seafood spicy noodle - good;; noodle  cooked a bit too long especially this as soaked in soup
Dumpling - not good

Can return for the first 2 dish.

One of the most authentic Korean restaurants in JB! We  ordered jjajangï¼Œ samgyetang, and tangsuyuk & Our favorite is the samgyetang as its taste really authentic. Fast food served and lady boss offered to refilled small dishes.  Big portions. Definitely will come back again.

Great quality of food. Proper black bean noodles and run by a Korean Boss and friendly service staff from Myanmar.

Authentic and relaxing atmosphere. Perfect for a family dinner with the kids or a meal and beers with the bros.

Food is nice and portion is big
